11#include "src/byte_parser.h"

17namespace webm {
18
19// Spec reference:
20// http://matroska.org/technical/specs/index.html#Targets
21// http://www.webmproject.org/docs/container/#Targets
22class TargetsParser : public MasterValueParser<Targets> {
23 public:
24 TargetsParser()
25 : MasterValueParser<Targets>(
26 MakeChild<UnsignedIntParser>(Id::kTargetTypeValue,
27 &Targets::type_value),
28 MakeChild<StringParser>(Id::kTargetType, &Targets::type),
29 MakeChild<UnsignedIntParser>(Id::kTagTrackUid,
30 &Targets::track_uids)) {}
31};
32
33} // namespace webm

35#endif // SRC_TARGETS_PARSER_H_
